{
  "_provenance": "[VERIFIED-OBSERVED] Teleporter/location name vocabulary extracted from three client TP-list memory dumps captured while the original MRA server was live. These are player-known teleport rosters as delivered by the original server (bulk-loaded at login via packet 0x21; incrementally added via server->client 0x35 'You now know'). NOT derived from MRA.exe \u2014 the client binary holds the list-management code but contains no names.",
  "_extraction": "NUL-delimited ASCII tokens from offset 13 (after the 13-byte dump header), charset [A-Za-z0-9_+/-], min length 2, scan halted at the first adjacent-memory binary token. 'RETURN' is intentionally absent: the client prepends it locally at login (FUN_0040743c ~0x4078) and the server never transmits it.",
  "_dumps": {
    "DUMP": {
      "md5": "de0b81aa50c9ef3a26abf88b421a9868",
      "size": 10336,
